Date-filter for current week, current month and current year:
current-week : {date-filter:track:last view date|minValue=-6d|maxValue=+1d|required=true|format=dd-MMM-yyyy}
current-month : {date-filter:track:last view date|minValue=-1m|maxValue=+1d|required=true|format=dd-MMM-yyyy} 
current-year : {date-filter:track:last view date|minValue=-1y|maxValue=+1d|required=true|format=dd-MMM-yyyy} 


The sample code for the current week and current month is mentioned here:
{code}
{report-table:maxResults=25}
{content-reporter:space=@self|type=attachment}
{text-filter:content:file name|exclude=.*jpeg,.*gif,.*jpg,.*GIF,.*JPG,.*png,.*PNG}
{date-filter:track:last view date|minValue=-6d|maxValue=+1d|required=true|format=dd-MMM-yyyy}
{number-sort:track:view count|order=desc}
{content-reporter}
{report-column:title=Title}{report-info:content:title|link=true}{report-column}
{report-column:title=Type}{report-info:attachment:content type}{report-column}
{report-table}  

